snippet.title: RARE first Pokémon Red and Green Japanese commercial EVER HD
snippet.description:
The first Japanese commercial about Pokémon, for the first time in high quality!
An ambigous girl talks to some weird old guys about this "new" game, Pokémon. You can also see the really weird old artworks, quite creepy, in my opinion. 
Enjoy!

NOTE: all credits go to Nintendo, Game Freak, Pokémon Inc. and their affiliates. I DO NOT own anything about Nintendo or the Pokémon franchise.
